<p><div class="geshifilter"><div class="javascript geshifilter-javascript" style="font-family:monospace;">$<span style="color: #000000;">&#40;</span>document<span style="color: #000000;">&#41;</span>.<span style="color: #000000;">ready</span><span style="color: #000000;">&#40;</span><span style="color: #0600FF;">function</span><span style="color: #000000;">&#40;</span><span style="color: #000000;">&#41;</span><span style="color: #000000;">&#123;</span><br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $<span style="color: #000000;">&#40;</span><span style="color: #ff0000;">&quot;#content-slider&quot;</span><span style="color: #000000;">&#41;</span>.<span style="color: #000000;">slider</span><span style="color: #000000;">&#40;</span><span style="color: #000000;">&#123;</span> animate<span style="color: #000000;">:</span> <span style="color: #0600FF;">true</span><span style="color: #000000;">,</span> change<span style="color: #000000;">:</span> handleSliderChange<span style="color: #000000;">,</span> slide<span style="color: #000000;">:</span> handleSliderSlide <span style="color: #000000;">&#125;</span><span style="color: #000000;">&#41;</span><span style="color: #000000;">;</span><br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="color: #0600FF;">var</span> content_scroll_pos <span style="color: #000000;">=</span> Math.<span style="color: #000000;">floor</span><span style="color: #000000;">&#40;</span><span style="color: #000000;">&#40;</span>$<span style="color: #000000;">&#40;</span><span style="color: #ff0000;">&quot;#content-scroll&quot;</span><span style="color: #000000;">&#41;</span>.<span style="color: #000000;">scrollLeft</span><span style="color: #000000;">&#40;</span><span style="color: #000000;">&#41;</span> <span style="color: #000000;">/</span> $<span style="color: #000000;">&#40;</span><span style="color: #ff0000;">&quot;#content-scroll&quot;</span><span style="color: #000000;">&#41;</span>.<span style="color: #000000;">width</span><span style="color: #000000;">&#40;</span><span style="color: #000000;">&#41;</span><span style="color: #000000;">&#41;</span> <span style="color: #000000;">*</span> <span style="color: #000000;">100</span><span style="color: #000000;">&#41;</span><span style="color: #000000;">;</span><br />
