        <div style="width:430px;overflow:auto;overflow-y:hidden;">
          <p>At first glance, the URL syntax is incorrect.  You have:</p>
<p><div class="geshifilter"><div class="text geshifilter-text" style="font-family:monospace;">http:www...</div></div></p>
<p>Where it should be</p>
<p><div class="geshifilter"><div class="text geshifilter-text" style="font-family:monospace;">http://www...</div></div></p>
<p>You forgot the set of slashes after the http.</p>
        </div>
