      </td>
      <td class="comment-body">
        <div style="width:380px;overflow:auto;overflow-y:hidden;">
          <p>Kevin, I've found this tutorial and tried to adapt it to a vertical slider bar.  I saw your comment and followed it, but my slider still doesn't slide.  The content scrolls, but the slider doesn't move.  Here's my code, do you see what could be the problem?</p>
